                                        <li><strong>Insufficient funds:</strong> Ensure your account has enough balance</li>
                                        <li><strong>Bank security:</strong> Your bank may have blocked the transaction - contact them</li>
                                        <li><strong>Billing address:</strong> Make sure your billing address matches your card</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                                
                                <!-- Support -->
                                <div class="content-section">
                                    <h2>üí¨ Need help?</h2>
                                    <p>
                                        Our support team is here to help! If you're experiencing technical issues or need assistance,
                                        <a href="mailto:support@bizzin.co.za" style="color: #EA7A57;">contact support</a> and we'll get you sorted quickly.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                                
                                <!-- Footer Message -->
                                <div style="border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 32px 0 0 0; padding: 24px 0 0 0; text-align: center;">
                                    <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
                                        Thanks for being a valued Bizzin member. We're here to support your entrepreneurial journey!
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                                
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                    
                    <!-- Footer -->
                    <div class="footer">
                        <table role="presentation" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                            <tr>
